OL,5, Former Royal Mail chairman Allan       
OL,6, Leighton has said the Horizon scandal  
OL,7, is "unbelievable" and "terrible".      
OL,9,FMr Leighton apologised for "elements"  
OL,10,Fof the scandal that occurred during his
OL,11,Ftime in the role.                      
OL,13,FEarlier, a former Post Office          
OL,14,Finvestigator also apologised for not   
OL,15,Fprobing reported problems with the     
OL,16,FHorizon IT system, blaming cost.       
OL,18,FBut ex sub-postmaster Seema Misra, who 
OL,19,Fhe investigated, said apologies "don't 
OL,20,Fmake any difference".                  
